"{\"key\":\"fact-opencode-agents-cannot-be-ported-has-4-predefined-types-onl\",\"type\":\"fact\",\"content\":\"OpenCode agents cannot be ported. Has 4 predefined types only: AgentCoder, AgentTask, AgentSummarizer, AgentTitle. Can configure models/parameters but cannot register new agent types. Skills are not an open standard in OpenCode - use custom commands or MCP tools instead.\",\"source\":\"user\",\"tags\":[\"fact\",\"model\",\"config\"],\"ts\":1771035461,\"bead\":\"bdcompound-18w\"}"
