"{\"key\":\"learned-compatibility-verification-complete-all-22-tests-passing\",\"type\":\"learned\",\"content\":\"Compatibility verification complete. All 22 tests passing: (1) path traversal blocked, (2) oversized files rejected (>10MB), (3) malicious YAML blocked (SAFE_SCHEMA), (4) template injection prevented, (5) file permissions correct (644/755/444), (6) model name validation working, (7) platform flags validated, (8) symlink detection verified, (9) conversion outputs verified, (10) format compatibility confirmed. Created SECURITY_TEST_RESULTS.md documenting all findings.\",\"source\":\"user\",\"tags\":[\"learned\",\"security\",\"test\",\"model\",\"schema\",\"validation\"],\"ts\":1771039480,\"bead\":\"bdcompound-xr3\"}"
