"{\"key\":\"learned-implemented-secure-conversion-scripts-with-all-security-cont\",\"type\":\"learned\",\"content\":\"Implemented secure conversion scripts with all security controls: (1) path traversal protection via validatePath(), (2) 10MB file size limits, (3) YAML SAFE_SCHEMA parsing, (4) template injection prevention (escape {{ }} before conversion), (5) explicit file permissions 644/755/444, (6) model name allowlist validation, (7) exact dependency pinning. All 21 security tests passing.\",\"source\":\"user\",\"tags\":[\"learned\",\"security\",\"test\",\"model\",\"schema\",\"validation\"],\"ts\":1771038942,\"bead\":\"bdcompound-b36\"}"
