"{\"key\":\"learned-opencode-tool-execute-after-fires-with-tool-task-when-subage\",\"type\":\"learned\",\"content\":\"OpenCode tool.execute.after fires with tool=task when subagent completes. Payload includes metadata.summary (tool call summary), metadata.sessionID, and output (final text). This is the correct mapping for SubagentStop - NOT session.idle. Cannot block completion (post-execution hook) but can inspect transcript and inject reminders.\",\"source\":\"user\",\"tags\":[\"learned\"],\"ts\":1771033458,\"bead\":\"bdcompound-0k4\"}"
"{\"key\":\"learned-plan-review-found-1-move-posttooluse-filtering-to-typescr\",\"type\":\"learned\",\"content\":\"Plan review found: (1) move PostToolUse filtering to TypeScript before spawning shell to avoid hot-path subprocess overhead, (2) security needs shell template injection fix - use Bun.spawn not dollar-sign shell, (3) simplicity reviewers recommend collapsing 5 tasks to 2 and using vanilla JS instead of TypeScript, (4) archive file grows unbounded - needs time-based archival\",\"source\":\"user\",\"tags\":[\"learned\",\"security\",\"fix\",\"typescript\"],\"ts\":1771032851,\"bead\":\"bdcompound-18w\"}"
